{"tid":562961,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：iOS用戶最討厭同Android用戶約會","createTime":"2018-02-16T12:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T07:35:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"15830128f4b680c79bbac2365c37e970ba3dea37","tid":562961,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"Lawton<br />\n<br />\n情人節剛過，在海外有不少單身人士利用交友 App 約會。但根據一項調查指出，用戶對於約會的對象，在約會期間操作電話有不同的看法，而且對方使用的機款式，更會影響約會後留下的印象。 <br />\n<br />\n外國交友網站《<a href=\"http://Match.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMatch.com&d=y8Uj6sQNro%2FuKFV%2B%2B0MCuL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=153fe409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Match.com</a>》在 2016 年年尾以 5509 名 18 至 70 歲的單身男女作為調查對象，在電話層面上，探討他們對約會對象的看法。在調查結果顯示到有 75％ 受訪者不喜歡對方在沒有給予解釋前接聽電話，而不喜歡對方在約會途中使用手機的受訪者有 58％。 <br />\n更有趣的是，有 92％ 的女性不喜歡約會對象使用比她們所持的更舊款的智能機，或許男士們下次約會要買過台新機。調查亦顯示，iOS 用戶對 Android 用戶做負面評價的機會率，比平均水平高出 21 倍；但 Android 用戶對 iOS 用戶投負面評價的機會率亦會比平均水平高 15 倍。 <br />\n但令人意料之外，只有 14％ 受訪者討厭對方在使用軟鍵盤輸入文字時發出嘀嘀聲。"},{"pid":"278ba7c17994cba2cd9024a788e4418d260468d5","tid":562961,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfb2fce4d771355bef57186857151937800a2f9","tid":562961,"uid":53730,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"即係iOS用戶多啲歧視人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f34d70b67d44fdc69f4bdda662011b7ac9b21c8","tid":562961,"uid":78622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:15:13.000Z","msg":"Airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb772a0bb227c720371bef1a399fc5031ee229